uk.ac.ebi.kraken.interfaces.uniprot.description

Interface Name

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HasEvidences, Serializable

    public interface Name
extends HasEvidences, Serializable
    Maps the Names of a protein in a DE line : RecName, AltName, SubName

    As an example: 
       ...
 DE   RecName: Full=Interleukin-2; 
 DE            Short=IL-2;         
 DE   AltName: Full=T-cell growth factor; 
 DE            Short=TCGF;                
 DE   AltName: INN=Aldesleukin;           

      ...
    See NameType for a a list of the allowable names. See FieldType for a list of the allowable fields.
